{"tid":2508393,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"莫少聰西裝滿摺痕  網民質疑冇錢買衫","createTime":"2021-04-28T17:18:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-28T23:36:49.000Z","uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"14294cc6e285e8d4e0d15417f24ac83665551667","tid":2508393,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T17:18:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2940000/2943493/20_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2940000%2F2943493%2F20_600.jpg&h=c2f7375a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n條褲幾似金仔 🙄"},{"pid":"541b5aeac3db6e799a97110dc557e9e883220443","tid":2508393,"uid":44730,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T17:18:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/UwA450A0ETs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FUwA450A0ETs&d=DgCTbN7XbHZJJfbPUwNNzbktNrE0CDS5yYjP391fFHI%3D&h=1aec3fca\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/UwA450A0ETs</a><br />\n諗起佢玩肚餓 🙄"},{"pid":"35f65ede3fb39dd39d36af1b7b51a5a65f61b6c4","tid":2508393,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T17:18:45.000Z","msg":"60歲的莫少聰憑一雙大眼及俊俏臉孔，在1980年代電影黃金期，算是「一代男神」，1988年放映的《中國最後一個太監》亦是他電影代表作。莫少聰早年已移居大陸生活，他的樣貌亦隨之「進化」不少，加上步入「登六」之齡，若然日久失修欠保養，只可以說天生靚樣亦返魂乏術。"},{"pid":"639ef9cf7d6ed7b9422c7e4b7dc4e232b2dcc720","tid":2508393,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T17:19:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2940000/2943493/19_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2940000%2F2943493%2F19_600.jpg&h=e2946105&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n莫少聰於商業活動上演出，西裝未熨燙好定係fashion嚟？網民指感覺寒酸。"},{"pid":"a93877b0a724148804732d4ce5beb7665be126c8","tid":2508393,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T17:19:18.000Z","msg":"日前影到莫少聰在一個商業活動上演出，惹起網民熱諷，指他西裝衣不稱身，打扮略見寒酸。有眼利網民指莫少聰身上的黑西裝滿布摺痕，完全沒有熨燙過，另西裝尺碼不合身，同時感覺他發福不少；再近距離看他容貌，雖然仍有「招牌大眼」，但雙目沒有神采又有大眼袋，加埋臉部膠味甚濃，老態畢露。<br />\n<br />\n網民慨嘆當年「一代男神」走晒樣，淪落至如斯此境地，紛紛留言「沒錢買衣服嗎，混的這地步」、「這身衣服是臨時翻出來的嗎？都沒來得及熨一下」，更猜測他一身裝束加起來應不超過300元，亦有抵死網民笑指莫少聰手上的「大鑽戒」可能價值不菲。"},{"pid":"56d5996bd1a211301953048d7f41643a2132256b","tid":2508393,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T17:19:54.000Z","msg":"莫少聰屬於早一批到大陸賺「人仔」的港星，在2011年時與年紀比他小28年的大陸歌手孫雲玲結婚，婚後兩人育有一女莫芷嫣，現已10歲。不過夫妻關係只維持5年便告終，女兒跟著父親生活。近年莫少聰幕前演出不多，只靠拍抖音片，甚至接一些廉價商演來維持生計，網民亦替他感到欷歔。"},{"pid":"a8244351c9f29db275899ca3f00f59a74dc1a6ad","tid":2508393,"uid":154763,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T19:21:03.000Z","msg":"成功歸化為大陸民工"},{"pid":"2683776d756ebee1d1926aa1abcb44121388c5ca","tid":2508393,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T23:03:03.000Z","msg":"其實點解太監會係代表作，記得85年拍過錯體人做主角，係咪太年輕冇人識 🙄"},{"pid":"b1d66b298a307139928245d3edeb66dda697fda2","tid":2508393,"uid":35166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T23:05:02.000Z","msg":"60歲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc24b227bac0b2960d92c0cb61a59f4b41f16273","tid":2508393,"uid":10757,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T23:24:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真心唔識 好紅架？"},{"pid":"473b276d356501df19a91769503dc4f8fedbdc85","tid":2508393,"uid":211461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T23:27:50.000Z","msg":"2021年仲著3粒鈕西裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afc6e07a59e26cf55b7657168bdb883349b007b8","tid":2508393,"uid":28237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T23:30:27.000Z","msg":"屌親啲女都係正嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff424357512438ccdf3